if pagination
	.model-paging
		p.records Showing
			select.pagination.form-control
				- for (var i = 0; i < pages; i++)
					if page === i+1
						option(value=i+1, selected)= i+1
					else
						option(value=i+1)= i+1
		| of #{pages} pages.
		div.page-size
			span Show
			select.pagination-size.form-control
				- for ps in pageSizes
					if pageSize === ps
						option(value=ps, selected)= ps
					else
						option(value=ps)= ps
			span records per page.
